title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.20.08
description:
I DO DOPE WITH DADDY:
---------------------
    Father-Daughter bonding gone terribly wrong... Mariah&#039;s father and older sister are terribly addicted to heroin and painkillers. It&#039;s gotten so bad, she&#039;s had to witness cops busting in her door, people shooting at her house, and her sister prostituting for drugs. Mariah&#039;s had to live with it for all these years, but now she&#039;s out of hope, and Steve&#039;s her last chance. But can Steve be the one to finally stand up to her family and save them from a bleak future?

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
